{"lemma":"زَلَمَيْ","slug":"زَلَمَيْ","root":"ز.ل.م","root_slug":"ز-ل-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ل-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18044","n18047","n18048","n18049"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut off a bit of, to pare off, to take the edge from, to concinnate by levigating"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut off a bit of, to pare off, to take the edge from, to concinnate by levigating"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of زَلَمَ (zalama) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"arrow without head and feathers","examples":[{"text":"يَا أَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ آمَنُوا إِنَّمَا ٱلْخَمْرُ وَٱلْمَيْسِرُ وَٱلْأَنْصَابُ وَٱلْأَزْلَامُ رِجْسٌ مِنْ عَمَلِ ٱلشَّيْطَانِ فَٱجْتَنِبُوهُ لَعَلَّكُمْ تُفْلِحُونَ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cloven hoof, or the projecting part behind it"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hyrax"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18044","headword_ar":"زَلَمَ","root":"zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalomN","text_ar":"زَلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut off"},{"kind":"text","text":"one's nose [and app. anything projecting, or prominent: see 2: and see also 8]. (ISh, K.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"his gift"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small, in quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amount;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) [as though he cut off something from it;] in [some of the copies of] the S, [but not so in mine,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zl~m","text_ar":"زلّم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filled"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) a water-ing-trough, or tank, (S,) or a vessel; (K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zl~m","text_ar":"زلّم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazoliymN","text_ar":"تَزْلِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AHn, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n18047","headword_ar":"زَلْمٌ","root":"zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulomN","text_ar":"زُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", whence the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa AlEabodu zalomFA","text_ar":"هُوَ العَبْدُ زَلْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalomap","text_ar":"زَلْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n18048","headword_ar":"زَلَمٌ","root":"zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulamN","text_ar":"زُلَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An arrow without a head and without feathers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azolaAmN","text_ar":"اَزْلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh, Msb, K:) which was applied to those ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divining-"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arrows by means of which the Arabs in the Time of Ignorance sought to know what was allotted to them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) they were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arrows upon which the Arabs in the Time of Ignorance wrote"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Command"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prohibition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"” (Mgh, Msb;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon some of which was written"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My Lord hath commanded me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and upon some,"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My Lord hath forbidden me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"” (Har p. 465;) or they were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three arrows; upon one of which was written"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My Lord hath commanded me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and upon another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My Lord hath forbidden me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the third was blank;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in v. 4;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and they put them in a receptacle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and when any one of them desired to make a journey, or to accomplish a want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he desired to perform some affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put his hand into that receptacle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and took forth an arrow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and if the arrow upon which was"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Command"},{"kind":"text","text":"” [or “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My Lord hath commanded me"},{"kind":"text","text":"” (Har ubi suprà)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came forth, he went to accomplish his purpose; but if that upon which was"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prohibition"},{"kind":"text","text":"” [or “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My Lord hath forbidden me"},{"kind":"text","text":"” (Har)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came forth, he refrained;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and if the blank came forth, they shuffled them a second time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd ubi suprà:) or, as some say, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AzlAm","text_ar":"ازلام"},{"kind":"text","text":"were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white pebbles, upon which they thus wrote, and by means of which they sought to know what was allotted to them in the manner expl. above:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har ubi suprà:) or, accord. to Az, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AzlAm","text_ar":"ازلام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arrows that"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belonged to Kureysh, in the Time of Ignorance, upon which were written"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hath commanded"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hath forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thou"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thou not;"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they had been well shaped"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zul~imato","text_ar":"زُلِّمَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and made even, and placed in the Kaabeh, the ministers of the House taking care of them; and when a man desired to go on a journey, or to marry, he came to the minister, and said,"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Take thou forth for me a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zlm","text_ar":"زلم"},{"kind":"text","text":"; ”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and thereupon he would take it forth, and look at it; and if the arrow of command came forth, he went to accomplish that which he had purposed to do; but if the arrow of prohibition came forth, he refrained from that which he desired to do:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[it is said that]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there were seven of the arrows thus called with the minister of the Kaabeh, having marks upon them, and used for this purpose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel in v. 4:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and sometimes there were with the man two such arrows, which he put into his sword-case; and when he desired to seek the knowledge of what was allotted to him, he took forth one of them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Some say that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azolaAm","text_ar":"اَزْلَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"are The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arrows of the game called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almayosir","text_ar":"المَيْسِر"},{"kind":"text","text":": but this is a mistake. (TA.) The seeking to obtain the knowledge of what is allotted to one by means of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AzlAm","text_ar":"ازلام"},{"kind":"text","text":"is forbidden in the Kur v. 4. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azolaAmu Albaqarapi","text_ar":"اَزْلَامُ البَقَرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The legs of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"[wild]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ox"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"likened to the arrows called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AzlAm","text_ar":"ازلام"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of their slenderness: or, accord. to the A, because of their strength and hardness. (TA.) [Hence, likewise,] the former of the two words ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalamN","text_ar":"زَلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") signifies also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A strong and light"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active boy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. as above: (TA:) [app. because] a poet likens [such] a boy to an arrow of the kind thus called. (S, TA. *)       -A2-  Also, both words, (K,) the latter on the authority of Kr, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cloven hoof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) accord. to some, peculiarly of the ox-kind: (TA:) or the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"projecting"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that is behind it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) pl. as above. (K, * TA.)       -A3-  And the latter of the same two words, (AA, S,) or each of them, (K,) [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hyrax Syriacus;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"animals called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wibaAr","text_ar":"وِبَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waborN","text_ar":"وَبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: pl. as above. (AA, S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","Har","TA","AA"]},{"entry_id":"n18049","headword_ar":"زُلَمٌ","root":"zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, throughout."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}